01847f43e97ade547302f765cdea598b03","tid":159751,"uid":50577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:55:28.000Z","msg":"巴打我讀新聞系，間唔中會出去做校內實習，可能見過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw想問你對呢行前景點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩忠告比第時入呢行既人"},{"pid":"19c9acb8b01b5de33ae9f8d2fd804043eefc997e","tid":159751,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:56:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做過邊單最勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牛頭角迷你倉<br />\n由朝到晚都係下面擺<br />\n不斷吸個d毒煙同氣</blockquote><br />\n好鬼攰 又唔知幾時有野拍又唔可以走開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果急屎去左屙 咁岩又有勁野影 <br />\n但係你屙緊屎MISS左咁點算</blockquote><br />\n通常冇乜必要都唔會離開部機<br />\n真係頂唔順就擺好個位<br />\n叫記者有咩事就禁個rec start制<br />\n不過風險都好高可免則免</blockquote><br />\n但係有時真係急屎都無計架喎<br />\n個個影到得你影唔到係咪會好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1cb633e01a579b79e52600f06b007dc38d5edde","tid":159751,"uid":22712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:59:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打我讀新聞系，間唔中會出去做校內實習，可能見過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw想問你對呢行前景點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩忠告比第時入呢行既人</blockquote><br />\n前景就普遍 新聞呢行好廣泛<br />\n有紙媒、傳媒、網媒等等<br />\n工唔怕搵唔到 但長遠睇要升職都唔易<br />\n眼見好多做做下記者會轉行做pr<br />\n<br />\n我好欣賞做記者既個種精神<br />\n做一個好既報導係可以改變好多社會睇法<br />\n加油 雖然好辛苦但我相信值得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6bace29c5c645e4256668c7f8bc65eb71e0471","tid":159751,"uid":22712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:01:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做過邊單最勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牛頭角迷你倉<br />\n由朝到晚都係下面擺<br />\n不斷吸個d毒煙同氣</blockquote><br />\n好鬼攰 又唔知幾時有野拍又唔可以走開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果急屎去左屙 咁岩又有勁野影 <br />\n但係你屙緊屎MISS左咁點算</blockquote><br />\n通常冇乜必要都唔會離開部機<br />\n真係頂唔順就擺好個位<br />\n叫記者有咩事就禁個rec start制<br />\n不過風險都好高可免則免</blockquote><br />\n但係有時真係急屎都無計架喎<br />\n個個影到得你影唔到係咪會好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n影唔到準備比阿頭屌屎忽<br />\n新聞唔同拍戲 冇take 2<br />\n由其是如果係做大台甩左<br />\n真係除時會抄魷魚（好似係）"},{"pid":"7a5aa5689a4d3c3e70ebdc9434d0a1be7cf9b8f8","tid":159751,"uid":69792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:08:13.000Z","msg":"之前part time做過財經，悶到抽筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fde28c897cc472dcdee3e5e64059a688f80809","tid":159751,"uid":67395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:10:08.000Z","msg":"有冇得介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6dd8c20e46e8cf2195870bed308e0b9e66e740","tid":159751,"uid":22712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前part time做過財經，悶到抽筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好悶 每日對數字又要分析<br />\n但做財仔好處就係新年個陣執利是<br />\n封封100 試過最好搵一日收4-5百利是<br />\n大公司搞業績會係四季香格搞<br />\n可以飲下咖啡食下茶點都唔錯"},{"pid":"36f7baa44425dab02c00f13c13c71c3fc16029ea","tid":159751,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊個女記者最黑人憎?</blockquote><br />\n我公司大部分都幾好人同幾靚既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁一定唔係大台<br />\n個撚個都臭西咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939aacc64ca7bca44c58a2da399498dd663772b7","tid":159751,"uid":22712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇得介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/